cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper is related to natural language processing and machine learning, which are covered by several sub-categories in arXiv CS. cs.CL (Computation and Language) is the most likely category as it specifically deals with language-related tasks. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes a deep learning method. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as aspect-level sentiment analysis is a sub-task of opinion mining, which is related to information retrieval. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a broad category that covers various aspects of AI, including natural language processing and machine learning. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is less likely but still possible as the paper uses word embeddings, which are also used in computer vision tasks.
